    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_02_01-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "今のは、私達のことを\n好きになっちゃう\n縁結びのおまじないだコン\nこれで一年……っ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is the spell of\nmatchmaking that makes you\nfall in love with us-kong\nwith this‚ for the rest of… ugh…",
