    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_02_01-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "ま、待って、やっぱり\nおかしいわよ……！\nなんで新年のご挨拶で\nおまじないをかける必要が",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-Wait‚ that's still weird…!\nWhy do we need to cast a spell\nas the New Year greetings",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.4256245812,
      "endTime": 60.8365771493,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_02_01-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "あ～～、瑠依ちゃん可愛い！\nほんま最高や！\nく～！　写真だけやなくて\n動画も保存したい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah~~‚ Rui-chan‚ so cute!\nYou're awesome!\nCool~!\nI want to leave a record not\nonly in photos but also in videos!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.9099134327,
      "endTime": 70.2666723132,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_02_01-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "ねぇ、瑠依ちゃん\n優ちゃん。言い辛いんだけど\nもう{user}\nさん来てるよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ Rui-chan‚ Yu-chan.\nIt's hard to say‚ but\n{user}-san\nis already here‚ you know?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.6303009233,
      "endTime": 77.4666743477,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_02_01-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ！？　す、すみません\n{user}さん\n今のは違うんです。もぉ\n優に化かされた気分だわ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eeh!? S-Sorry‚\n{user}-san\nThis is a misunderstanding.\nReally‚ I've been teased by Yu…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.7046581151,
      "endTime": 86.6666779082,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_02_01-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、新年早々、瑠依ちゃん\nの可愛い姿が見れて\n{user}さんも\n嬉しいやろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚ from the beginning of\nthe New Year‚ we can see\nRui-chan's cute point\nAre you happy too‚\n{user}-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.8650236331,
      "endTime": 93.6000112415,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_02_01-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "それを言うなら、新年から\n{user}さんに\n頑張る姿を\n見てもらえるなんて\nすっごく嬉しいけどね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you say so‚ we can show\n{user}-san\nhow hard we're working\nfrom New Year\nThat's really nice‚ I think",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.8906700018,
      "endTime": 101.8333445749,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_02_01-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "そうね、今日の収録も……\nいえ、これから一年間\n私達のことを、一番近くで\n見守っていて下さいね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ today's recording….\nNo‚ for the rest of the year‚\nplease keep watching us\nfrom the closest place",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.1163841449,
      "endTime": 111.8666779082,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_02_01-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "ふふふ、必要やったら、他の\n子に目移りせえへんように\n\nおまじないかけたるからな？\nほな、改めて――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufufu‚ if needed‚ should I put\na spell on you so you can't look\nat other girls?\nThen‚ once again――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.2212365034,
      "endTime": 122.0333445748,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "今年も\nよろしくお願いします！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I look forward to your continued\ngoodwill in the coming year!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.4370645089,
